msgstr "Kompatibilitet med girara 0.4.3"

#: data/org.pwmt.zathura.metainfo.xml.in:239
msgid ""
"Remove highlight-transparency setting. Set the alpha component of highlight-"
"color, highlight-active-color and highlight-fg instead."
msgstr ""
"Ta bort highlight-transparency setting. Set the alpha component of highlight-"
"color, highlight-active-color and highlight-fg instead."

#: data/org.pwmt.zathura.metainfo.xml.in:240
msgid "Remove smooth-reload setting. Smooth reloading is now always enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta bort inställningen smooth-reload. Mjuk omladdning är nu alltid aktiverad."

#: data/org.pwmt.zathura.metainfo.xml.in:241
msgid ""
"Remove plain database backend. The sqlite database backend imports the data "
"from the plain database the first time. sqlite is now a hard dependency."
msgstr ""
"Ta bort plain database backend. The sqlite database backend imports the data "
"from the plain database the first time. sqlite is now a hard dependency."

#: data/org.pwmt.zathura.metainfo.xml.in:242
msgid "Fix a segfault if dbus is not enabled."
msgstr "Åtgärda en segmenteringskrasch om dbus inte är aktiverat."

